snippet.title: Super Stone Legacy Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Stone Legacy is a Hack N' Slash Bullet Hell with RPG classes available for the PC. Inspired by the arcade game play of the 80/90s, Super Stone Legacy is multiplayer, bright, and difficult!

Procedurally generated content keeps the action fresh as you and your friends battle hordes of enemies to save the world.

Check out our website:
www.SuperStoneLegacy.com

Love to hear from ya!
@GreedDevblog
